            "body": "> Which tests specifically? \r\n\r\nMostly the 'shellslash' tests. What even is the point of 'shellslash' if it isn't respected by `expand()` etc.?\r\n\r\n> I don't see much reason to display options or buffer names with platform-specific slashes\r\n\r\nWhat do you mean by \"display\"?",
