        {
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "> What do you mean by \"display\"?\r\n\r\n- For options: the actual value (and everywhere it is displayed, e.g. `:set`).\r\n- For buffers: in statusline, and anywhere else where mixed slashes was already possible. \r\n    - Example: if it's possible for `bufname()` to return mixed slashes, then it's safe for us to always return `/` slashes because there was never a guarantee of only `\\` slashes.",
